      "source": "6300系",
      "translation": "6300 Series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI6300}.description",
      "source": "旧式化した6000系置き換えと、東急目黒線相互乗り入れを目的に導入された車両。",
      "translation": "Rolling stock introduced to replace the aging 6000 Series and for mutual through-service with the Tokyu Meguro Line."
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOKYU3000}.name",
