    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOKYU3000}.type",
      "source": "3000系",
      "translation": "3000 Series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOKYU3000}.description",
      "source": "都営三田線・東京メトロ南北線乗り入れに際し導入された車両。",
      "translation": "A train introduced for through service on the Toei Mita Line and Tokyo Metro Namboku Line."
