    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI10300}.description",
      "source": "老朽化した10-000系一部編成の置き換えのため登場した車両。",
      "translation": "A train introduced to replace some aging 10-000 Series sets."
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI10300R}.name",
