    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI10300R}.description",
      "source": "老朽化した10-000系編成のうち、経年の激しい先頭車のみを10-300系と同系の車両に交換したもの。",
      "translation": "Among the aging 10-000 Series sets, only the heavily deteriorated lead cars were replaced with vehicles of the same series as the 10-300 Series."
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI12000E}.name",
