      "translation": "12-000 Series (Early Model)"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI12000E}.description",
      "source": "都営大江戸線のうち、練馬-光が丘間の部分開業時に製造された車両。",
      "translation": "A train manufactured for the Toei Oedo Line during the partial opening of the Nerima-Hikarigaoka section."
