      "translation": "Oedo Line"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI12000L}.company",
      "source": "東京都交通局",
      "translation": "Tokyo Metropolitan Bureau of Transportation"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI12000L}.type",
      "source": "12-000系",
      "translation": "12-000 Series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI12000L}.description",
      "source": "都営大江戸線の車両。初期型と違い無塗装車体である。",
      "translation": "A Toei Oedo Line train. Unlike the initial model, it has an unpainted car body."
