    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TOEI5300}.description",
      "source": "都営浅草線の旧型車置き換え・冷房化を目的として導入された車両。空港間連絡列車などにも利用される。",
      "translation": "A train introduced to replace older cars and provide air conditioning on the Toei Asakusa Line. Also used for airport connecting trains."
